Name: Fisher's Chowder
AttributesDescription: Increases DEF and Max HP of all Resonators in the team by 10% and 20% respectively, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: A thick soup made with fish and dried Sea Flytraps simmered in milk. People in the coastal areas love this hearty and rich dish. With the cold wind blowing in from the sea, what dish could beat a bowl of hot soup?
